@startuml
autonumber
actor "ATCC" as ATCC
participant ":System" as System

activate ATCC
ATCC -> System : searchAlternativeRoutes(originIataCode, destinationIataCode)
activate System

note right of System: The system searches for direct routes between\nthe two airports and also calculates one-stop\nalternative routes by combining existing active routes.

System --> ATCC : returns direct routes and one-stop alternative route chains
deactivate System
deactivate ATCC
@enduml
